<paragraph blockId="38.[151,1146,1293,1356]" box="[151,1146,1329,1356]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">
(adapted from 
<bibRefCitation author="Cadena-Castaneda, O. J. &amp; Gorochov, A. V." box="[316,740,1329,1355]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39" pagination="189 - 203" refId="ref39416" refString="Cadena-Castaneda, O. J. &amp; Gorochov, A. V. (2013) Review of the Neotropical genera Quiva and Yungasacris (Orthoptera: Tettigoniidae: Phaneropterinae). Zoosystematica Rossica, 22 (2), 189 - 203." type="journal article" year="2013">Cadena-Castañeda &amp; Gorochov, 2013</bibRefCitation>
