<bibRefCitation author="Rehn, J. A. G." box="[1326,1436,1750,1772]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39" pagination="271 - 319" refId="ref42693" refString="Rehn, J. A. G. (1950 [1949]) Studies in the Group Dysoniae (Aphidniae of authors) (Orthoptera: Tettigoniidae: Phaneropterinae) Part I. Transactions of the American Entomological Society, 75 (3 - 4), 271 - 319." type="journal article" year="1950">Rehn, 1950</bibRefCitation>
