<figureCitation box="[820,907,1926,1948]" captionStart="FIGURE 22" captionStartId="38.[151,250,1114,1138]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,310,1090]" captionTargetId="figure-80@38.[151,1436,309,1091]" captionTargetPageId="38" captionText="FIGURE 22. Quiva species. A–D. Q. (P.) angieae. E–H. Q. (Q.) pulchella. I–K. Q. (Q.) diaphana. L–N. Q. (Q.) buhrnheimi. O–Q. Q. (Q.) sharovi. R–T. Q. (Q.) abacata. U–W. Q. (Q.) gutjahrae. A, E. Male habitus in lateral view. B, F, I, L, O, R, U. Frons. C, G, J, M, P, S, V. Subgenital plates. D, H, K, N, Q, T, W. Cerci." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6876267" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6876267/files/figure.png" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Fig. 22N</figureCitation>
